         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Leodamas to Theodorus, greeting. I have paid over(?) to the State 1834 2/3 artabae of olyra. Do you therefore leave this olyra for yourself and measure out the rest to Lysimachus, that it may be...Good bye. The 2{.}th year...(Addressed) To Theodorus. (Grenfell &amp; Hunt)</ab>
         </div>
